steps for deploying a static website on S3

- required services => AWS S3 and Route53
- on Route 53 register a domain to use for the static website (.click is cheaper)
- go to S3 service
- create a bucket with the same name as the registered domain name
- once bucket is created click the bucket to enter inside
- click on properties and scroll to the bottom to enable static hosting
- go to permissions and put a bucket policy
- upload the website files required
- once upload is done go to the